abstract: Pandas is the Swiss-Multipurpose Knife for Data Analysis in Python. In this talk we will look deeper into how to gain productivity utilizing Pandas powerful indexing and make advanced analytics a piece of cake. Pandas features multiple index types. This talk will give you a deep insight into the Pandas indexes and showcase the handiness of special Indexes as the TimeSeriesIndex.
